# Cursor AI Rules for IDIT

## Working Directory
The Next.js project is in the `idit` subfolder. Always run commands from:
c:\Users\pauls\OneDrive\Projekte\IntexSystemPrototype\idit

## Dev Server
- Only one dev server on port 3000
- To restart: Get-Process -Name "node" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force; npm run dev
- Use background mode

## Language
All UI must be in German (Deutsch).

## Stack
- Next.js 16 (App Router)
- Prisma 5 (SQLite)
- Better Auth
- Tailwind CSS v4
- TypeScript
